  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. ",
    "Add the onion and cook until caramelized, about 5 minutes. ",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute. ",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes. ",
    "Add the Massaman curry paste and cook for 1 minute. ",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring to a simmer. ",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook for 10 minutes. ",
    "Stir in lime juice, salt, and black pepper. ",
    "Warm the ti-leaf wraps according to package instructions. ",
    "Assemble the wraps by spooning the chicken and curry mixture onto the center of each wrap, followed by cilantro and peanuts. "
